about.summary: A tiny LRU cache implementation and decorator

name: repoze.lru
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "repoze.lru" %}
{% set version = "0.7" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0429a75e19380e4ed50c0694e26ac8819b4ea7851ee1fc7583c8572db80aff77

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vvv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - setuptools

test:
  imports:
    - repoze
    - repoze.lru

about:
  home: http://www.repoze.org
  license: BSD Modification Variant
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: A tiny LRU cache implementation and decorator
  dev_url: https://github.com/repoze/repoze.lru

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - nicoddemus
